---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 330
  - Title: Ingwa Sûtra
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
  - 859
---
If you want to know the Karma causes which belong to the past, look at
the Karma effects which belong to the present. If you want to see the
Karma effects as they will appear in the future, look well to the
causes operating here and now.
